                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/7597</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Simpich</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nogales, Arizona</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-04-15T17:00:00-07:23">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 15, 1916, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Telegraphic reports to Calles say family of John Lehr captured in November by
                    Yaquis has been rescued by General Martinez and will be returned first
                    opportunity to Lehr at Saqui Grande. District continues quiet. Agents report
                    Cananea and Ensanada orderly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Simpich</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
